Package: Rcssplot
Title: Customization of plots using cascading style sheets
Version: 0.1.1.0
Authors@R: person("Tomasz", "Konopka", , "tokonopka@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Tomasz Konopka <tokonopka@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Tomasz Konopka <tokonopka@gmail.com>
Description: Rcssplot brings cascading style sheets to the R graphical
    environment. It provides a means to separate the aesthetics from the data
    crunching in plots and charts.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.2)
Imports:
    graphics,
    stats,
    utils
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
License: GPL-2
LazyData: true
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
